### 9. Staff Views Attendees List for an Event

# Retrieve the list of users who purchased tickets for a specific assigned event.
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/event/{{eventId}}/attendees?page=1&limit=50&search=&status=
Authorization: Bearer {{staffToken}}


### 9b. Staff Views Attendees List for a Course
# Retrieve the list of users who enrolled in a specific assigned course.
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/course/{{courseId}}/attendees?page=1&limit=50&search=&status=
Authorization: Bearer {{staffToken}}